{"tid":108405,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"挑戰 Amazon、Netflix！Apple 將製作原創內容","createTime":"2017-02-05T08:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T11:40:44.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8f3ede8756d923d28ee3816b7119adb10024a2","tid":108405,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"美劇和綜藝節目選擇越來越多，質素亦越來越高，原因之一可能是串流平台的興起，平台都需要製作獨家的原創內容以爭取觀眾支持。《The Grand Tour》就是一個好例子，這個有史以來製作費最高的汽車節目，是 Amazon Prime 的重點綜藝節目項目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14h8Ex1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14h8Ex1.jpg&h=62dfd8c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/02/05/apple-consider-produce-own-tv-program/hottopic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2Fapple-consider-produce-own-tv-program%2Fhottopic%2F&d=Ru8OiKpQtXbNv5YRwinC6sKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=51021cd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/02/05/apple-consider-produce-own-tv-program/hottopic/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前 Apple CEO Tim Cook 暗示，Apple TV 未來會在集團的內容訂閱中扮演重要角色，為集團帶來更多收入，其中一個方向就是仿效 Amazon 和 Netflix 製作自家原創內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。Apple 透過旗下音樂平台 Apple Music 製作了一些原創節目，這些內容會在今年稍後時間陸續推出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。以 Apple Music 試水溫後，Apple 會從中吸收經驗，以此作為製作 Apple TV 原創內容的起點。Cook 表示他們對 Apple TV 平台有更多的計劃，會在未來一年慢慢推出，而製作原創電視節目亦在考慮之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"d5de780a7ab32b2a3cd28d5365ae78fc6fe9b2ec","tid":108405,"uid":26266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"人地電視業真係百花齊放，香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p